query:
INSERT INTO reserved_funds (
              id,
              amount,
              actual_amount,
              status,
              created_at,
              updated_at
          )
          SELECT 
              id,
              amt,
              actual_amte,
              stat,
              NOW(),
              NOW()
          FROM UNNEST(
              $1::bigint[],
              $2::bigint[],
              $3::bigint[],
              $4::fund_status[]
          ) AS t(id, amt, actual_amte, stat)
          ON CONFLICT (id) DO UPDATE
          SET amount = EXCLUDED.amount,
              actual_amount = EXCLUDED.actual_amount,
              status = EXCLUDED.status,
              updated_at = NOW();
